d decision\u2011making, and crew cooperation\u2014Candidate\u202fB remains the most well\u2011rounded and safest option for a long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
